    "About CPC",
    "The Centre for Professional Communication (CPC) conducts communication modules which are incorporated in SIT degree programmes. Modules are designed to think critically and develop effective communication skills for both their studies and future workplace.",
    "What we do",
    "CPC offers customized critical thinking and communication courses to enhance the communication knowledge and skills of SIT undergraduate and postgraduate students.",
    "The Centre also conducts continuing education and training (CET) programmes for working professionals, as well as customised corporate training for organisations who wish to upgrade their employees' communication skills to stay relevant and competitive in the business environment.",
    "Working closely with industry partners and other universities, our faculty conducts research in diverse fields, as well as consults and develops innovative communication solutions.",
